PyHumod INSTALL
===============

 Installation from the latest source code:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  $ hg clone https://pyhumod.googlecode.com/hg/ pyhumod
  $ cd pyhumod
  $ sudo python setup install
  
 Installation of version 0.01:
 ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  $ wget http://pyhumod.googlecode.com/files/pyhumod-0.01.tar.gz
  $ tar xzf pyhumod-*.tar.gz
  $ cd pyhumod-*
  $ sudo python setup.py install

 Notes:
 ~~~~~~
 * It's important that the conf/humod file is copied to /etc/ppp/peers,
   otherwise the Modem.connect() method will fail.
   
